{"tid":870821,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"張超雄今年六十一歲，首次在香港置業","createTime":"2018-10-21T12:06:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-21T14:55:31.000Z","uid":173617,"like":36,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"2e0a468239fe3b204162cf4f1a7a5214895b1192","tid":870821,"uid":173617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T12:06:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/nextplus/magazine/article/20180708/2_601441_0/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Fnextplus%2Fmagazine%2Farticle%2F20180708%2F2_601441_0%2F&d=JVMmNnZrY845v6GXxerBpMPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=d3b90fe2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Fnextplus%2Fmagazine%2Farticle%2F20180708%2F2_601441_0%2F&h=3b4cda4a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/nextplus/magazine/article/20180708/2_601441_0/</a><br />\n樓爆,篇文今年7月,估佢早兩個月買,正值樓價最高位,條友做左多年淡友,租屋無啦啦走去買樓,一買就最高位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bc5bb6a25fc25f2691c03d3fa6b9166452064e5","tid":870821,"uid":51920,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T12:09:33.000Z","msg":"燈撚過大師"},{"pid":"2fdc5b140901a5e8b3d477f9012d9d59da4c54c2","tid":870821,"uid":122318,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T12:09:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/21/200942_d78e8a753fc5ade84e0b5f10d46bc7b1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F21%2F200942_d78e8a753fc5ade84e0b5f10d46bc7b1.png&h=7b2b6802&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"038b713e3748c0bc27de65c881f04082282b3d53","tid":870821,"uid":173617,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T12:11:37.000Z","msg":"香港樓市是龐氏騙局，只要心存公義都難以認同。是什麼驅使張超雄跪低？是愛？是責任？「<span style=\"color: red;\">嚟緊會進入收入減少嘅狀態。如果仲要交租， 唔知交到幾時。</span>」他去年從理大應用社會科學系的教職退休，立法會還有兩年才換屆，趁著議員的薪津可通過壓力測試，還是快快趕上尾班車，「我僅僅仲申請到mortgage。如果冇mortgage，更加唔使買樓啦。」<br />\n<br />\n供樓至八十歲，又是時候做逆按揭，想想都覺抑鬱。<br />\n<br />\n跌10%,夠租4-5年啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a529e2c679e02886eb236bd1cda97e2cf2d9be3d","tid":870821,"uid":51933,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T12:13:59.000Z","msg":"難民報應"},{"pid":"9c9b2189e10d08d81f098d380c116845e9d7b71e","tid":870821,"uid":89225,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T12:18:18.000Z","msg":"議員+教授做咁多年都買唔到樓咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7af8c5f67c5acce47e790fe14337fda66045110","tid":870821,"uid":51920,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T12:40:37.000Z","msg":"讓堆公屋出黎 比班蝻住晒<br />\n自己就供貴樓<br />\n偉大過耶穌<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b195f015a493d97c528dd17bb8bd82aaef442cf","tid":870821,"uid":62646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T12:43:16.000Z","msg":"難民之父好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ccd8215ac2d8c3c99c59e1538b577b36f4681d8","tid":870821,"uid":75877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T12:44:50.000Z","msg":"難民之父摸頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c27c215dd6c15859828ac02460fda0e43a1d629c","tid":870821,"uid":46933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T12:46:34.000Z","msg":"要帶多幾多個難民先夠供樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dd1066177d5801500b97a6b205daaebe4961e99","tid":870821,"uid":38194,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T12